242
00:19:19,800 --> 00:19:23,400
   

243
00:19:34,615 --> 00:19:36,895
You drank all night?

244
00:19:36,895 --> 00:19:41,595
I didn't drink much. We went to the KTV and then had breakfast.

245
00:19:41,595 --> 00:19:44,100
All you do is play.

246
00:19:44,100 --> 00:19:46,900
Where are you going? Working overtime?

247
00:19:46,900 --> 00:19:49,600
What for? I'm getting fired.

248
00:19:49,600 --> 00:19:53,300
Because of what happened yesterday? Chill.

249
00:19:53,300 --> 00:19:57,000
Just get her a gift. She's a middle-aged lady.

250
00:19:57,000 --> 00:20:02,200
Get her some pricy creams or tonics. She can't be mean to you.

251
00:20:02,200 --> 00:20:05,100
Save it. Wash up and sleep.

252
00:20:05,100 --> 00:20:08,600
- Where are you going? 
 - I'll see some apartments.

253
00:20:08,600 --> 00:20:11,400
